## Did we find bacteria from human excretions?

Yes! All bacterial species in @tbl-bacteria were detected in the monitoring and are also documented to come from the human gastrointestinal track or other bodily fluids. The most well-known of which is *Escherichia coli*, although there are many more species of bacteria living inside our bodies.

